rukon - admin interface for riak

# features

 - Display contents of bucket
 - Display contents of document on click
 - Edit contents of the document (json.object)
 - Delete individual documents or all docs of a bucket

# Usage

    git clone git://github.com/jmetzner/rukon
    ./upload.sh *
    open http://localhost:8098/riak/rukon/index.html?bucket (change buucket to the bucket name you want to open)

